FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1779019866
OL,3,CGnomes to feature at Chelsea Flower
OL,4,CShow as stars decorate garden
OL,5,Cfavourites
OL,7,FPeople will be able to bid to get
OL,8,Ftheir hands on the gnomes, which are
OL,9,Fdecorated by celebrities including
OL,10,FAlan Titchmarsh, Dame Mary Berry, Tom
OL,11,FAllen, Dame Joanna Lumley and Bill
OL,12,FBailey, in an online auction from
OL,13,FFriday until Sunday May 24.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1779019866
OL,3,CGnomes to feature at Chelsea Flower
OL,4,CShow as stars decorate garden
OL,5,Cfavourites
OL,7,FMoney raised in the auction will go to
OL,8,Fthe RHS's Campaign For School
OL,9,FGardening, which helps schoolchildren
OL,10,Faccess gardening, giving them the
OL,11,Fchance to learn through growing
OL,12,Fplants, developing practical skills,
OL,13,Fconfidence and understanding of the
OL,14,Fenvironment, the charity said.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1779019866
OL,3,CGnomes to feature at Chelsea Flower
OL,4,CShow as stars decorate garden
OL,5,Cfavourites
OL,7,FAnd visitors to the show will also be
OL,8,Fable to spot one or two of the cheery
OL,9,Fchaps in the RHS And The King's
OL,10,FFoundation Curious Garden, designed
OL,11,Fwith input from Charles, Sir David
OL,12,FBeckham and Mr Titchmarsh to a bid to
OL,13,Fencourage people to get curious about
OL,14,Fgardening.
OL,16,FThe appearance of gnomes in the garden
OL,17,Fwill reflect a tradition at Highgrove
OL,18,FGarden, the King's residence in
OL,19,FGloucestershire, where a gnome is
OL,20,Foften to be found in The Stumpery.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
