FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1779019866
OL,3,CGnomes to feature at Chelsea Flower
OL,4,CShow as stars decorate garden
OL,5,Cfavourites
OL,7,FIt is only the second time the RHS has
OL,8,Flifted its Chelsea gnome ban, after
OL,9,Ffirst allowing them in 2013 to
OL,10,Fcelebrate the centenary of the show.
OL,12,FClare Matterson, RHS director general,
OL,13,Fsaid: "We are delighted to lift the
OL,14,Fban on gnomes for such an important
OL,15,Fcause.
OL,17,F"RHS Chelsea is our biggest charitable
OL,18,Ffundraiser, and this auction will
OL,19,Fenable us to support thousands of
OL,20,Fchildren to discover the joy and
OL,21,Fbenefits of gardening.
OL,26,@uD@GOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1779019866
OL,3,CGnomes to feature at Chelsea Flower
OL,4,CShow as stars decorate garden
OL,5,Cfavourites
OL,7,F"My heartfelt thanks go to all our
OL,8,Fcelebrity contributors, whose
OL,9,Fcolourful gnomes will not only
OL,10,Fbrighten the show but also help
OL,11,Finspire a lifelong connection with
OL,12,Fgardening for young people."
OL,14,FThe RHS unveiled its celebrity gnomes
OL,15,Fas it announced the Chelsea Flower
OL,16,FShow sold out before opening its doors
OL,17,Fto the public for the first time since
OL,18,Fbefore Covid, which forced the
OL,19,Fcancellation of the event at the Royal
OL,20,FHospital, Chelsea, in 2020, and a move
OL,21,Fto an autumn slot in 2021.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@\O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
