PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1779019866
OL,3,CGnomes to feature at Chelsea Flower
OL,4,CShow as stars decorate garden
OL,5,Cfavourites
OL,7,FMs Matterson said the news the show
OL,8,Fwas already sold out was "great for
OL,9,Fgardening".
OL,11,FThe 150,000 tickets help raise
OL,12,Fmillions of pounds for community
OL,13,Fgardening programmes across the UK and
OL,14,Fscience research to inform efforts to
OL,15,Ftackle climate change, the charity
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,26,@pD@ZOUqD@JO]
